<br>
I moved here for serveral reasons, one being i was not enjoying a server with a population of 5000+, ever tried to xp in BoT with 60+ people in it?, or PoN with 80+? <br>
Its hard and the grief that comes with it is immense. I pay my money to enjoy this game and having to share a camp that is meant for 1 group, split between 3 is NOT fun. Another reason was, as i hit lvl 60ish I realised i loved this game alot so wanted to try the High end so to speak. Now let me give you an insight to AB's &quot;High End&quot;<br>
<br>
Darkwind, probably the 4th highest in the game, is in PoTime. Shadows of Doom,Magus Amicita and Odyssy are all in or just about in Elemental planes, Tight Underpants (Yes i know <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  ) are in Ssra Temple, Wind of Tranquility, Reconquista, Forsaken Ambition and a few more ar in NToV. This means anything that pops has an estimated life expentancy of 1 hour...yes 1. Within that time 1-2 guilds will amass to kill it, what ensues is called a &quot;race&quot;. Where the first guild to prep and engage the mob gets the right to kill, if they wipe they forefit to the next one. Now sounds ideal, but durign this time, some (not all) guilds will /ooc or /shout insults or try to provoke the other guild, also some guilds will go as low as training a guild as they engage or turning the mob a wrong way, and will wipe they other guild. <br>
(Imagine 4 IB and 3 or 4 Named dragons being pulled to you by &quot;accident&quot; while you engage Klandicar)<br>
<br>
This leads to a game which is more hassle than skill, you run to a zone only to be KS'd or lose a target due to lack of people on, its not fun.Not saying you should get free rights to a mob, but comon..racing for Vindi a 8hour mob is a bit silly, or being forced to kill lower mobs (bottom feed) just because you lack things to kill and then sell loot because noone needs it, but that guild that arrived after you could of used.<br>
<br>
Another reason I moved is because i have RL friends here, are you saying I am not welcomed to play here with MY friends just because I choose a Euro server thinking it would be more suited?<br>
<br>
I lost alot moving here, friends, equipment, money, 64 levels and a year and a half amasses alot of these thigns =/ but i still moved, and so far love it, people are nice, its intresting to see people RP, though I myself do not partake of it, I woouldnt stop someone engaging in it, does what I do with my time really bother you, If i choose to raid, unless you decide to RP with say the Emp Ssra and pull his friends on me, then likely we would have no problems.<br>
<br>
 I have no reason to speak &quot;l33t&quot; even though after 1 1/2 years i have seen much of it, maybe as a joke to my friends i would after a big kill, but no i am not going to run up to you a say &quot;d00d sow plz&quot; why do it? it makes no sense and makes people look stupid, its funny...once.<br>
